<paragraph id="7F5A1705A498F91DC83E97438CDE6B68" pageId="11" pageNumber="26">1 M holotype (MNHN N° RS8669), Khnifiss lagoon (approx. 27.93°, -12.34°), Tarfaya, Morocco. Paratypes: 2 F (MNHN N° RS8670), from the same locality.</paragraph>
